=Love Me in Three Days=

2
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:21,780
=Episode 22=

3
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:28,120
Luoluo!

4
00:00:30,680 --> 00:00:32,280
Why are you here suddenly?

5
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:34,040
Didn't you enter the production already?

6
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,520
