9
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:49,360
I knew it's fake.

10
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:54,320
Do I still stand a chance?

11
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:58,160
Luoluo.

12
00:01:00,720 --> 00:01:04,360
Do you think it's possible for us?

13
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,920
It's fake that I'm getting married
to your brother,

14
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:20,000
but I do love him.

15
