Wait for me. I'll go get something.

81
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,040
It's just down there. I'm not leaving.

82
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:50,860
Step aside.

83
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,080
Here. Give me your hand.

84
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:05,000
Be careful. Slowly.

85
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:08,520
Stop crying. Your makeup is gone.

86
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,760
It's okay now. I...

87
